---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Vermietler"
  description="Privacy policy for Vermietler. How we collect, use, and protect your data in accordance with the GDPR (DSGVO)."
>
  <Navbar lang="en" />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <header>
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: April 13, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose mt-10 max-w-none prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-brand-500 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline prose-p:text-gray-600 prose-li:text-gray-600 prose-strong:text-gray-900">

        <h2>1. Controller</h2>
        <p>The controller responsible for data processing on this website is:</p>
        <p>
          Abiodun Samuel<br />
          Glockenturmstraße 30<br />
          14055 Berlin, Germany<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@vermietler.com">info@vermietler.com</a>
        </p>

        <h2>2. Overview of data processing</h2>
        <p>We process personal data only to the extent necessary to provide a functional website and our free calculators. We process data in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR/DSGVO) and the German Bundesdatenschutzgesetz (BDSG).</p>

        <h2>3. Data we collect</h2>

        <h3>3.1 Calculator usage data</h3>
        <p>When you use our free calculators (mortgage, closing costs, rental yield, depreciation, rent brake), we collect anonymous usage data to understand how the tools are used and to improve them. This includes the values you enter into the calculators and the calculated results.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Data collected:</strong> Calculator type, input values (e.g. purchase price, interest rate, selected German state), calculated results, language preference</li>
          <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> Product improvement and understanding which features are most valuable</li>
          <li><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in improving our tools)</li>
          <li><strong>Third party:</strong> PostHog (see Section 4.1)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Calculator inputs do not include personally identifiable information. No names, addresses, or financial account details are collected.</p>

        <h2>4. Analytics and tracking</h2>

        <h3>4.1 PostHog</h3>
        <p>We use <strong>PostHog</strong> for website analytics and product usage tracking. PostHog is hosted in the European Union (EU) at <code>eu.i.posthog.com</code>. PostHog collects:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pages visited and interaction events</li>
          <li>Calculator usage data (as described in Section 3.1)</li>
          <li>Device type, browser, operating system</li>
          <li>Approximate location (derived from IP address, which is anonymised)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>PostHog is configured in <strong>"identified_only"</strong> mode, meaning anonymous visitors are not assigned persistent person profiles.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Provider:</strong> PostHog, Inc. (2261 Market Street #4008, San Francisco, CA 94114, USA)</li>
          <li><strong>Data location:</strong> European Union</li>
          <li><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in understanding website usage)</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy policy:</strong> <a href="https://posthog.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">posthog.com/privacy</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Third-party services</h2>

        <h3>5.1 Tawk.to live chat</h3>
        <p>We use the live chat service <strong>Tawk.to</strong> to answer visitor enquiries directly on the website. When you load a page, the chat widget is loaded from Tawk.to's servers, establishing a connection between your browser and Tawk.to. This processes technical connection data (in particular your IP address) and chat content (when you actively use the chat).</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Provider:</strong> tawk.to inc. (187 East Warm Springs Rd, SB298, Las Vegas, NV 89119, USA)</li>
          <li><strong>Data location:</strong> EU/USA (international transfers based on Standard Contractual Clauses pursuant to Art. 46 GDPR)</li>
          <li><strong>Data collected:</strong> IP address, device data, chat history, name and email address (only if voluntarily provided in the chat)</li>
          <li><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in providing direct communication with website visitors)</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy policy:</strong> <a href="https://www.tawk.to/data-protection/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tawk.to/data-protection</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.2 Google Fonts</h3>
        <p>This website loads typefaces (DM Sans, Space Grotesk) from <strong>Google Fonts</strong>, a service provided by Google Ireland Limited. When you visit a page, your browser establishes a connection to Google's servers to download the font files. This transmits your IP address to Google.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Provider:</strong> Google Ireland Limited (Gordon House, Barrow Street, Dublin 4, Ireland)</li>
          <li><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in consistent and efficient typography)</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy policy:</strong> <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">policies.google.com/privacy</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website does not set first-party cookies. PostHog and Tawk.to may set cookies or use local storage to maintain session and chat information. No advertising or marketing cookies are used.</p>

        <h2>7. Your rights under GDPR</h2>
        <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Right of access</strong> (Art. 15 GDPR): You can request information about whether and what personal data we process about you.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> (Art. 16 GDPR): You can request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> (Art. 17 GDPR): You can request deletion of your data, provided no legal obligation requires retention.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to restriction of processing</strong> (Art. 18 GDPR): You can request that we limit processing of your data in certain circumstances.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong> (Art. 20 GDPR): You can request your data in a structured, machine-readable format.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to object</strong> (Art. 21 GDPR): You can object to processing based on legitimate interest at any time.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to withdraw consent</strong> (Art. 7(3) GDPR): You can withdraw any consent you have given at any time, without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@vermietler.com">info@vermietler.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>8. Right to lodge a complaint</h2>
        <p>You have the right to lodge a complaint with a data protection supervisory authority. The competent authority for Berlin is:</p>
        <p>
          Berliner Beauftragte für Datenschutz und Informationsfreiheit<br />
          Alt-Moabit 59-61<br />
          10555 Berlin<br />
          <a href="https://www.datenschutz-berlin.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.datenschutz-berlin.de</a>
        </p>

        <h2>9. SSL/TLS encryption</h2>
        <p>This site uses SSL/TLS encryption for security reasons and to protect the transmission of confidential information, such as inquiries that you send to us as the site operator. You can recognize an encrypted connection by the fact that the browser's address bar changes from "http://" to "https://" and by the lock symbol in your browser's address bar.</p>
        <p>When SSL or TLS encryption is enabled, the data you send to us cannot be read by third parties.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to this privacy policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy to reflect changes in our data processing practices or legal requirements. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates the most recent revision. We recommend reviewing this page periodically.</p>

      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
